"title": "8813: riches, spiritual",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8813",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Out of his infinite abundance God gives his people spiritual treasure. This, much more valuable than material wealth, is to be held in the highest esteem and sought after eagerly.</p>\n<h2>The riches of God</h2>\n<h3>His wisdom and knowledge</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:33-Rom11:36\">ROM 11:33–11:36</a></strong></p>\n<h3>His mercy, love and grace</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:4\">EPH 2:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:8\">EPH 3:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:4\">ROM 2:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:7\">EPH 2:7</a></p>\n<h3>His riches in Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:2-Col2:3\">COL 2:2–2:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:19\">PHP 4:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:27\">COL 1:27</a></p>\n<h2>God bestows spiritual riches on believers</h2>\n<h3>His precious word</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job23:12\">JOB 23:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:9-Ps19:10\">PSA 19:9–19:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:72\">PSA 119:72</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:111\">PSA 119:111</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:127\">PSA 119:127</a></p>\n<h3>A wealth of spiritual qualities</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa33:5-Isa33:6\">ISA 33:5–33:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov2:1-Prov2:5\">PRO 2:1–2:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:6\">PRO 15:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor9:10-2Cor9:11\">2CO 9:10–9:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:7-Eph1:8\">EPH 1:7–1:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:2-Col2:3\">COL 2:2–2:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:5\">JAS 2:5</a></p>\n<h3>A glorious gospel</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:7\">2CO 4:7</a></strong></p>\n<h3>A costly kingdom</h3>\n<p><em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:44-Matt13:46\">MAT 13:44–13:46</a></p>\n<h3>A rich reward</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth2:12\">RUT 2:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam26:23\">1SA 26:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:20\">PSA 18:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov25:21-Prov25:22\">PRO 25:21–25:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:24\">COL 3:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:35\">HEB 10:35</a></p>\n<h3>A heavenly inheritance</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:32\">ACT 20:32</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:13-Eph1:14\">EPH 1:13–1:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:18\">EPH 1:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:12\">COL 1:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:24\">COL 3:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:4\">1PE 1:4</a></p>\n<h2>Christians and spiritual riches</h2>\n<h3>Christians need to appreciate their spiritual riches</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:7-Eph1:8\">EPH 1:7–1:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:18\">EPH 1:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:9\">REV 2:9</a></p>\n<h3>Christians need to store up treasure in heaven</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:33\">LUK 12:33</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:20\">MAT 6:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:20-Luke12:21\">LUK 12:20–12:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:19\">1TI 6:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:26\">HEB 11:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:18\">REV 3:18</a></p>",
